description: This skill provides educational entertainment by providing fun facts about computers. Users can ask for a fact about computers and the skill will provide a random fact from its list of facts.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask computer facts to tell me a fact.
Alexa, ask computer facts to tell me a computer fact.
Alexa, ask computer facts to give me a fact.
name: computer facts
shortDescription: This skill provides fun facts about computers.
